changelog.release_notes:
v4.4 Update Notes:
1. fixed a bug that no response on first generation pebble occasionally;
2. optimization;

v4.2 Update Notes:
1. Weather support automatic location;
2. A new battery indicator is available, Christmas tree, some lights on the tree, the size of the light depends on battery level;
3. Custom fonts support English characters, not just numbers;

v4.1 Update Notes:
1. Three fonts can be set for numbers;
2. Support two weather data sources;
3. Position of battery level percent can be set to bottle's outside or inside;
3. Bluetooth disconnect alert can be enabled or disabled;

v3.1 Update Notes:
1. Added the battery level percentÔºõ
2. When the Bluetooth connection is interrupted, the custom text will show an alert, a vibration is also triggered;

v3.0 Update Notes:
1. Added the battery status indicator, you can disable;
2. Weather icon optimization, distinguish day and night;
3. Supports all square display watches (including Classic, Steel, Time, Time Steel, Pebble 2, Time 2);

